		<div>This is something that I've been emailed about a couple of times, and the above fix should work.  <br />
<br />
It seems like the people who are having this problem are all using it with the Vert2 sets.  I'm not sure how to keep it from happening, since if the positions and sizes exist in the user's ini file, it will use those instead of what's in the .xml file.  Anyone have any ideas?</div>
